# Web API Conventions

- Next.js App Router API routes (`apps/web/src/app/api/`)
- Database: Supabase PostgreSQL via `postgres` driver + Drizzle ORM
- Schema: `apps/web/src/lib/db/schema.ts`
- BigInt columns use `{ mode: "bigint" }` — must serialize as `.toString()` in responses
- `jsonResponse()` helper in `apps/web/src/lib/api/json-response.ts` handles BigInt serialization
- Auth: `verifyAdminKey()` in `apps/web/src/lib/auth.ts` (admin routes only)
- Package name: `@velthoryn/client` (NOT `@velthoryn/merkle`) for workspace Merkle SDK
- Workspace: `pnpm-workspace.yaml` lists `apps/*` only — must add `clients/*` before using workspace deps
- Security headers already configured in `next.config.ts` (X-Frame-Options, CSP, etc.)
- `.env.example` exists with all current vars

## Missing (as of Phase 00)

- No rate limiting
- No auth on POST routes (campaigns, root-versions, status, claims/sync)
- No CORS middleware
- `PATCH /api/campaigns/[treeAddress]/status` should be removed — status from indexer only
